{"tid":525104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[找數了]香港女神總會已將17-18季度上半程各級聯賽所籌募到既296元港幣善款捐左去慈善機構喇 #UNHCR #周末聯賽正式回歸","createTime":"2018-01-10T09:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T00:10:59.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c722e347d0d4d1d148a93bea1900674494d3d527","tid":525104,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=85cc4ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/172055_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F172055_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a9b25bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本會已經將上述$296善款捐往UNHCR，以行動幫助世界各地飽受戰火摧殘既苦困難民,為佢地送上一點祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThe Federation has donated the above $ 296 donation to UNHCR to help war-stricken hardship refugees across the world and send them a little bit of blessings <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外下半季賽程亦已喺較早前公佈,詳情可以留意返下面<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 17/18香港超級女神聯賽及其他級別歇冬期後詳細比賽秩序公佈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/518316\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/518316</a><br />\n<br />\nThank you for attention<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fe792c66bd01e9e6ed8ef64f3245aa8736e767","tid":525104,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /